<div style="font-family:'Archivo',sans-serif;font-weight:700;color:var(--navy);">Jim <span style="font-weight:400;color:var(--text-light);font-size:0.9rem;">— After-Hours Emergency Rental</span></div>
</div>
<p style="margin-bottom:32px;"><a href="https://search.google.com/local/reviews?placeid=ChIJe_gqTAjk_ocRVVpllXYH-zQ" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--navy);font-weight:600;">Read all reviews on Google →</a></p>

<h2>Beyond the festival</h2>
<p>The 15-passenger van isn't just for Cranberry Festival weekend. Groups using our vans throughout the year include:</p>
<ul style="margin-bottom:24px;padding-left:20px;">
<li style="margin-bottom:8px;"><strong>Wedding parties</strong> shuttling guests between venues and hotels</li>
<li style="margin-bottom:8px;"><strong>Family reunions</strong> covering large extended-family events</li>
<li style="margin-bottom:8px;"><strong>Sports teams</strong> traveling to tournaments throughout the Midwest</li>
<li style="margin-bottom:8px;"><strong>Church groups</strong> for retreats, conventions, and youth events</li>
<li style="margin-bottom:8px;"><strong>Corporate teams</strong> for offsites and group business travel</li>
<li style="margin-bottom:8px;"><strong>School trips</strong> when buses don't make sense for smaller groups</li>
</ul>
<p>If your group needs to be somewhere together and a couple of cars feels like too much logistics, the van is usually the answer.</p>

<h2>Make the call</h2>
<p>Festival is the last weekend of September. Vans book up by July. Reserve yours now while the calendar is still open.</p>
<p>Call <a href="tel:+17153961466"><strong>715-396-1466</strong></a> with your dates and we'll block off the van for your group. No deposit required to hold the reservation.</p>

<div style="margin-top:48px;">
<h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
<div class="faq-list">
<div class="faq-item">
<button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">When is the Warrens Cranberry Festival?
